This is a placeholder for pointer.png.
A real PNG image file for the wheel pointer should be placed here.
Due to tool limitations, an actual PNG image cannot be created automatically.
Consider using a CSS triangle for the #pointer element if a PNG is not available.
Example CSS for a triangle pointer:
#pointer {
    width: 0;
    height: 0;
    border-left: 25px solid transparent; /* Adjust size as needed */
    border-right: 25px solid transparent; /* Adjust size as needed */
    border-top: 35px solid #FFD700; /* Adjust color and size (this is pointer color) */
    position: absolute;
    top: -30px; /* Adjust position to point correctly */
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 3;
    /* Remove background-image properties if using this */
}
